      "markdown": "## B Doa survey\n\nPlease interview your friends and find out what they would like to do on special days.\n\n\n\nWhat's your favourite special day?\n\nWhat would you like to do?\n\nMy favourite special day is Teachers' Day. It's coming soon.I'd like to buy some flowers and make a card for my teacher.\n\nWould you like to make a phonecall or send a message?\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_903_1267_1462_1851.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"22%\" /></div>\n\n\nI'd like to callher.\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1536_1182_2265_1861.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"29%\" /></div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><html><body><table border=\"1\"><tr><td>name</td><td>Bill</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>special day</td><td>Teachers' Day</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>things he/she would like to do</td><td>buy some flowers make a card make a phone call</td><td></td><td></td></tr></table></body></html></div>\n\n\n## C Let's write\n\nWhat would you like to do on Spring Festival?",
